						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Launch-of-the-Cassava-Mechanisation-and-Agro-processing-Project-CAMAP" title="Launch of the Cassava Mechanisation and Agro-processing Project (CAMAP)" alt="link">Launch of the Cassava Mechanisation and Agro-processing Project (CAMAP)</a></h2>

	
					<p>The Cassava Mechanisation and Agro-processing Project (CAMAP) was launched early July 2013 at the National Centre for Agricultural Mechanisation, Nigeria.&nbsp; Coordinated by the African &nbsp;Agricultural Technology Foundation (AATF), CAMAP will enhance the contribution of cassava production and processing technologies for sustainable improvements in food security, incomes &nbsp;and livelihoods of farmers, processors, and marketers in the cassava sector. CAMAP will achieve this through upgrading and expanding traditional planting, harvesting and processing &nbsp;techniques, thus developing competitive cassava commodity value chains for a reliable supply of processed products for food and non-food industrial use.(AATF, 04/07/2013)</p>
							<p><span class="date">31/07/2013</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/Launch-of-the-Cassava-Mechanisation-and-Agro-processing-Project-CAMAP">Read more...</a>
</div>
<br class="cl">
